Package org.paukov.combinatorics

This package contains common classes and interfaces of the library such as ICombinatoricsVector, Generator and Factory.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ICombinatoricsVector<T> This interface is implemented by all generic combinatorics vectors of the library
IFilter<T> This is the interface for filtering the generated combinatorial vectors
IGenerator<T> This interface is implemented by all generic generators in the library
 

Class Summary
Factory This is the factory class to create combinatorics vectors and generators.
Generator<T> Abstract base class for all generic generators of the library
IntegerFactory This is a special factory to create integer vectors and generators
IntegerGenerator This is a special abstract class for all integer generators
IntegerVector This class represents a simple vector of elements of type int
 

Package org.paukov.combinatorics Description

This package contains common classes and interfaces of the library such as ICombinatoricsVector, Generator and Factory.
